  "special": {
    "description": "Fires 6 rounds per shot for the cost of 1 ammo, while keeping the usual Jakobs pistol critical-hit bonus.",
    "title": "Monty's wife don't take no guff."
  },
  "notes": "With the Two Fer accessory, each shot costs 2 ammo and releases 10 projectiles. It functions much like a Masher-style revolver, but with one fewer pellet. Its most common drop source is Mick Zaford, who is only available if you side with the Hodunks at the end of the Clan Wars chain. That choice locks you out of fighting Jimbo and Tector Hodunk, who have better odds of dropping the Slagga. You can still farm both in one run by saving and quitting after getting a Maggie from Mick before the mission becomes ready to turn in, which resets the side choice on reload.",
